snippet.title: Metal Gear 2: Solid Snake (PS3) - Metal Gear D Boss Fight Gameplay Playthrough (Part 12)
snippet.description:
GRAY FOX ataca SOLID SNAKE utilizando o novo Metal Gear D!

Gameplay / Playthrough / Longplay  de Metal Gear 2: Solid Snake, originalmente lançado para MSX2, desenvolvido e publicado pela Konami, contido em Metal Gear Solid 3: Snake Eater HD Edition de Playstation 3.

Complete  Playthrough Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rBhFkzL7i0A&list=PL_YL558gxlL82b9-dMoiQovKIKm-7JX9L
